<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Linux on grrru</title><link>https://grrru.github.io/categories/linux/</link><description>Recent content in Linux on grrru</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.152.2</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Sep 2025 11:25:00 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://grrru.github.io/categories/linux/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>리눅스 명령어</title><link>https://grrru.github.io/posts/2025-09-01-%EB%A6%AC%EB%88%85%EC%8A%A4-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Sep 2025 11:25:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://grrru.github.io/posts/2025-09-01-%EB%A6%AC%EB%88%85%EC%8A%A4-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="-1-os"&gt;✅ 1. OS&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cat /etc/os-release &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 배포판 이름/버전&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hostnamectl &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 호스트명, 커널, 머신 정보&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;uname -a &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 커널 정보&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="-2-cpu"&gt;✅ 2. CPU&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;lscpu &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CPU 정보 요약&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cat /proc/cpuinfo &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CPU 정보 상세&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;nproc &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 사용 가능한 CPU 개수&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="-3-메모리"&gt;✅ 3. 메모리&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;free -h &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 총/사용/가용 메모리&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cat /proc/meminfo &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 상세 메모리 지표&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vmstat &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 1초 간격으로 메모리/CPU/IO 상태 출력&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="-4-프로세스"&gt;✅ 4. 프로세스&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;htop &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 실시간 자원 사용 (htop 패키지 필요)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ps aux --sort&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;%mem &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 메모리 사용량 정렬해서 프로세스 출력&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>